3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the diffusion of information in networks, which is a key topic in the subfield of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper uses theoretical and numerical methods to study the diffusion of information, which is a key topic in the subfield of data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.CY (Cryptography and Security) - Although not the main focus of the paper, the diffusion of information in networks has implications for security and privacy, which are key topics in the subfield of cryptography and security.
